OL,3,CUnmasking the monster: Reclaiming a
OL,4,Cmother's truth from a father's lie
OL,6,FBack in 1991 in the scenic seaside
OL,7,Ftown of Castlerock, Colin Howell, a
OL,8,Fpillar of the community, a dentist and
OL,9,Fa father of four, arranged the dead
OL,10,Fbodies of his wife Lesley and his then
OL,11,Flover Hazel Stewart's husband RUC
OL,12,Fconstable Trevor Buchanan in a fume
OL,13,Ffilled car making what was in fact a
OL,14,Fcrime scene look like a suicide pact.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
