OL,3,CUnmasking the monster: Reclaiming a
OL,4,Cmother's truth from a father's lie
OL,6,FThe truth was only revealed in 2009,
OL,7,Falmost 20 years later, after Howell
OL,8,Fwalked into the a police station and
OL,9,Fconfessed to killing them. He
OL,10,Fimplicated Hazel Stewart, who at first
OL,11,Fdenied her involvement, claiming she
OL,12,Fwas under the control of the man with
OL,13,Fwhom she'd been having an affair but
OL,14,Fwho was later also found guilty of the
OL,15,Fdouble murder.
OL,17,FIt's a story that never ceases to
OL,18,Fshock. Still grabbing news headlines
OL,19,Fyears on from when the truth finally
OL,20,Femerged as Stewart continues to try to
OL,21,Fappeal her sentence.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
