OL,3,CUnmasking the monster: Reclaiming a
OL,4,Cmother's truth from a father's lie
OL,6,FIf as a journalist it's hard to begin
OL,7,Fto unpack, you can only begin to
OL,8,Fimagine what that's like for the
OL,9,Fchildren involved.
OL,11,FWhat they've endured and had to work
OL,12,Fthrough on so many levels is almost
OL,13,Funfathomable.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
