OL,3,CUnmasking the monster: Reclaiming a
OL,4,Cmother's truth from a father's lie
OL,6,FFor the Howells they admit there was a
OL,7,Freluctance to be part of the new
OL,8,Fdocumentary ITV's 'Killer in the
OL,9,FHouse' given the years they'd taken to
OL,10,Fprocess it all and the toll it might
OL,11,Ftake on their mental health but they
OL,12,Fdecided it was important to tell their
OL,13,Fversion of events, reclaim their
OL,14,Fmother's memory and help others
OL,15,Fdealing with trauma.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
