OL,3,CUnmasking the monster: Reclaiming a
OL,4,Cmother's truth from a father's lie
OL,6,FI had the privilege of interviewing
OL,7,Fone of Howell's sons Daniel who now
OL,8,Fcalls himself Seamus Daniel - to
OL,9,Freclaim his Irish identity. Given his
OL,10,Fmiddle name was James he thought it
OL,11,Ffitting.
OL,13,FFrom his apartment in New York where
OL,14,Fhe now lives and works as a doctor,
OL,15,FSeamus Daniel spoke with apparent ease
OL,16,Fand eloquence - no outward sign of the
OL,17,Fanguish he's experienced.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
