OL,3,CUnmasking the monster: Reclaiming a
OL,4,Cmother's truth from a father's lie
OL,6,FIt was on his second birthday that
OL,7,F'Colin', as his son refers to him
OL,8,Fduring the course of our interview,
OL,9,Fkilled his mother Lesley and Trevor
OL,10,FBuchanan. A lie his father lived with
OL,11,Ffor another 18 years.
OL,13,FSeamus described the shock, disbelief
OL,14,Fand anger he felt when he found out
OL,15,Fwhat actually happened, in particular
OL,16,Fthe hypocrisy of his seemingly
OL,17,Freligious father, someone he'd seen as
OL,18,Fa fraud for many years - even before
OL,19,Fthis.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
