OL,3,CUnmasking the monster: Reclaiming a
OL,4,Cmother's truth from a father's lie
OL,6,FAs I brought the interview to a close
OL,7,Fand thanked Seamus for sharing with
OL,8,Fus, he thanked me for my time, the
OL,9,Fprogramme makers and the people of the
OL,10,Fnorth coast for their love and support
OL,11,Fin the copious amounts of lasagne and
OL,12,Fpavlova they shared with the family in
OL,13,Fthe aftermath of his elder brother
OL,14,FMatthew's death and later when the
OL,15,Ftruth of what happened to his mother
OL,16,Fand Trevor came out and their lives
OL,17,Fimploded.
OL,19,FNot something he said he'd get in the
OL,20,FUS and for which we as a community
OL,21,Fshould be proud.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
