OL,3,CUnmasking the monster: Reclaiming a
OL,4,Cmother's truth from a father's lie
OL,6,FOff tape and in the interests of
OL,7,Fdisclosure I told Seamus my mum had
OL,8,Ftaught him and his little brother
OL,9,FJonathan at nursery school and he
OL,10,Fimmediately gave me the school's name
OL,11,Fand recalled that while he couldn't
OL,12,Fremember the teachers' faces he had
OL,13,Fvery happy memories of playing and
OL,14,Freading stories there. And he said to
OL,15,Fsay hi to her from him.
OL,17,FTheir childhoods may have been marred
OL,18,Fby tragedy but the Howell siblings
OL,19,Fhave proven they won't be defined by
OL,20,Ftheir past.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/11
